{"tid":90645,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"SUSE linux on Windows 10","createTime":"2017-01-22T09:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T11:32:12.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fbd23ec45032662a138ff15d86fcd5360c7504ca","tid":90645,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:09:58.000Z","msg":"You can now install SUSE Linux distribution inside WSL on Windows 10<br />\n<a href=\"https://mspoweruser.com/can-now-install-suse-linux-distribution-inside-wsl-windows-10/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmspoweruser.com%2Fcan-now-install-suse-linux-distribution-inside-wsl-windows-10%2F&d=LeNpBdcj6I5QCBKhB5VE%2BX8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=f86e8cff\" target=\"_blank\">https://mspoweruser.com/can-now-install-suse-linux-distribution-inside-wsl-windows-10/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-mspoweruser.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/WSL-SUSE-Linux.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn-mspoweruser.netdna-ssl.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FWSL-SUSE-Linux.png&h=7584bd23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位點睇？"},{"pid":"fe54d17c84ba1ceae921896e26a67d0fd9412eb2","tid":90645,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:13:34.000Z","msg":"Windows 10現已支援安裝openSUSE Linux<br />\n<br />\n之前微軟與Canonical達成合作協議並在Windows 10內置了Ubuntu子系統，支援使用Linux命令行工具等。<br />\n<br />\n如今開發者也可以選擇安裝使用openSUSE Linux啦，不過至少需要安裝64位版的Windows 10 週年更新才可以。<br />\n<br />\n如果你更喜歡該系統的話現在有個選擇：openSUSE Leap 42.2和SUSE Linux Enterprise Server 12 SP2。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣的Linux用戶可以按照下面的步驟在Windows 10 週年更新版本中安裝和啟用SUSE Linux操作系統。<br />\n<br />\n支那網慎入：<a href=\"https://www.landiannews.com/archives/29306.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.landiannews.com%2Farchives%2F29306.html&d=LeNpBdcj6I5QCBKhB5VE%2BX8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=24ac9e58\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.landiannews.com/archives/29306.html</a>"},{"pid":"b4e2d14fb6d4e0605eb69bde1c45e8934645adba","tid":90645,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T10:22:52.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係Fedora(好憎佢個SELinux安全功能)!<br />\nopenSUSE都好呀, 希望裝好後個terminal可以正常運作(佢魯味Ubuntu個LXDE既terminal唔能work, 迫我用番Unity!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )啦! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d744c5a0e584c5fcbd977bbc421853f564641e","tid":90645,"uid":61249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T10:38:35.000Z","msg":"用緊ubuntu wsl <br />\n其實唔錯 不過set 字體set 到嘔血"},{"pid":"3f642fb03243d1a30afbd5b178aeb4f99877d2ef","tid":90645,"uid":23699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T18:03:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊ubuntu wsl <br />\n其實唔錯 不過set 字體set 到嘔血</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我今日先dklm 嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對中文supoort完全係... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身中文隻字型係細明體7 到<br />\n<br />\n如果你用cmd開<br />\n首先要set個region 較做中文<br />\n咁要睇到有中文名既filename<br />\n<br />\n但副作用就係佢會幫你用中文字型<br />\n細明體 7到<br />\n然後較utf8 encoding 再轉 font<br />\n<br />\n好啦 我見powershell 有得行init script<br />\ndklm 無得用script set字型 得顏色<br />\n<br />\n最後個方法係開powershell ise<br />\n行start bash <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我見啲人話有得改個registery<br />\n但好似會crash唔敢試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed3ef7b361832ef0577242c81b9c65405525b0f","tid":90645,"uid":23699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T18:05:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用緊ubuntu wsl <br />\n其實唔錯 不過set 字體set 到嘔血</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我今日先dklm 嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對中文supoort完全係... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身中文隻字型係細明體7 到<br />\n<br />\n如果你用cmd開<br />\n首先要set個region 較做中文<br />\n咁要睇到有中文名既filename<br />\n<br />\n但副作用就係佢會幫你用中文字型<br />\n細明體 7到<br />\n然後較utf8 encoding 再轉 font<br />\n但佢唔會save低<br />\n<br />\n好啦 我見powershell 有得行init script<br />\ndklm 無得用script set字型 得顏色<br />\n<br />\n最後個方法係開powershell ise<br />\n因為佢default用utf 8開<br />\n行start bash <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我見啲人話有得改個registery<br />\n但好似會crash唔敢試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4c82bb566c045a70e22b9801c9cf39b9a8b9a862","tid":90645,"uid":61249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T01:02:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用緊ubuntu wsl <br />\n其實唔錯 不過set 字體set 到嘔血</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我今日先dklm 嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對中文supoort完全係... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身中文隻字型係細明體7 到<br />\n<br />\n如果你用cmd開<br />\n首先要set個region 較做中文<br />\n咁要睇到有中文名既filename<br />\n<br />\n但副作用就係佢會幫你用中文字型<br />\n細明體 7到<br />\n然後較utf8 encoding 再轉 font<br />\n<br />\n好啦 我見powershell 有得行init script<br />\ndklm 無得用script set字型 得顏色<br />\n<br />\n最後個方法係開powershell ise<br />\n行start bash <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我見啲人話有得改個registery<br />\n但好似會crash唔敢試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>